        <heading>2708.  Lessor's privilege over sublessee's movables</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2708.  Lessor's privilege over sublessee's movables
The lessor's privilege extends to the movables of the sublessee but only to the extent that the sublessee is indebted to his sublessor at the time the lessor exercises his right.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109772</p>
